import { useLayoutEffect } from 'react';
import cssVars from 'css-vars-ponyfill';

const isEmpty = (obj) => {
  if (obj === null || obj === undefined) {
    return true;
  }

  for (const prop in obj) {
    if (obj.hasOwnProperty(prop)) {
      return false;
    }
  }
  return JSON.stringify(obj) === JSON.stringify({});
}
